{
  "texts": [
    "Run the script on a GPU with at least 15 GB RAM to reproduce results in §5.",
    "It takes about 5 days on a T4 GPU.",
    "Training is performed using the transformers package (Wolf et al., 2020).",
    "The notebook analysis/dataset.ipynb can be run to (1) produce visualizations of the distributions of acc extra, acc test, and acc base (for each classification task and experiment configuration), and (2) compute p-values for the hypothesis test specified in (13).",
    "For all settings of m and n, no p-values were statistically significant at the 0.05 level."
  ]
}